{"tid":1033932,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"支那棍頭笑廣東話嗰個例子係啲懶音撚先會中伏，正音嘅廣東話根本無呢個問題","createTime":"2019-02-23T14:12:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-23T15:57:58.000Z","uid":11598,"like":50,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"87c4f28f94b5e8f228949c400d7b83e540a88026","tid":1033932,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T14:12:41.000Z","msg":"話說前排啲支那豬棍頭係度散播白色恐怖做鳩廣東話<br />\n整咗個好似急口令咁嘅短片<br />\n首先用普通話讀「各個國家有各個國家嘅國歌」<br />\n然後就用廣東話讀，啲懶音重到 讀到一pat 屎咁咯咯咯<br />\n然後就話廣東話係雀仔講嘢咁<br />\n睇見都火撚滾 啲講廣東話嘅人自己都講撚到一pat屎咁 無撚嘢呀？<br />\n讀正音嘅廣東話根本唔會有呢個問題<br />\n啲死棍頭為咗滅廣東話已經開始無所不用其極<br />\n將廣東話同柒掛勾 我屌你老母<br />\n如果你有懶音嘅問題 希望你可以去糾正返<br />\n唔好講乜嘢是但啦 咁執著做乜 <br />\n而家班棍頭已經開始軟硬兼施 唔好以為香港可以獨善其身<br />\n上連登呢代可能已經係最後一代香港人會講廣東話"},{"pid":"f0552301089ded6ae1c2a7e95345b10d23d351c0","tid":1033932,"uid":11598,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T14:12:52.000Z","msg":"講起都嬲 屌你老母"},{"pid":"d8d73afff5bbf8224f53b1cdf20dd5c33b05f203","tid":1033932,"uid":225846,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T14:14:16.000Z","msg":"支那話最難聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e765de985aa9bab097dceec9b654279474ad3b2b","tid":1033932,"uid":71092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T14:15:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74235c84cfa98deeed045afcd64090ddd591c8e4","tid":1033932,"uid":11598,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T14:21:28.000Z","msg":"大家應該覺得講廣東話係一種榮幸 係高尚 有深厚文化基礎<br />\n語言係文化嘅載體 廣東話係所謂「中華」文化嘅結晶 有大量古漢語詞匯用法都傳承咗落嚟<br />\n普通話完全係垃圾嚟 只係為咗穩固政權統一文化而推廣嘅一種方言"},{"pid":"f7641077fe4230dd23bd70654d89336e45e4a3cb","tid":1033932,"uid":11598,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T14:24:49.000Z","msg":"當共產黨係廣州推普滅粵<br />\n我冇出聲<br />\n因為我唔係廣州人<br />\n<br />\n當港共推行普教中<br />\n我冇出聲<br />\n因為我已經Grad咗<br />\n<br />\n當班細路開始返支那 玩抖陰 飲喜茶<br />\n我冇出聲<br />\n因為唔係我個仔<br />\n<br />\n當廣東話開始被孤立<br />\n<del><span style=\"font-size: small;\">我冇出聲</span></del><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">你仲唔撚出聲 等幾時？<br />\n屌你老母！</span></strong>"},{"pid":"3d1ea49ed78f77b70be1e53435c5e04ce919df19","tid":1033932,"uid":90820,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T14:26:42.000Z","msg":"但香港有班人連粵語都講唔正<br />\n淨係睇連登留言都知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你<span style=\"color: red;\">起</span>邊度？<br />\n係<span style=\"color: red;\">味</span>咁樣呀？<br />\n我<span style=\"color: red;\">呢家</span>打緊機"},{"pid":"6d2fcb28d0f2eb8fce116917d4504c212617b3c8","tid":1033932,"uid":11598,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3d1ea49ed78f77b70be1e53435c5e04ce919df19","tid":1033932,"uid":90820,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T14:26:42.000Z","msg":"但香港有班人連粵語都講唔正<br />\n淨係睇連登留言都知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你<span style=\"color: red;\">起</span>邊度？<br />\n係<span style=\"color: red;\">味</span>咁樣呀？<br />\n我<span style=\"color: red;\">呢家</span>打緊機"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T14:28:47.000Z","msg":"最撚難聽係 琴屹 <br />\n次次都想問佢講乜撚嘢呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n簡簡單單兩隻字 尋日 都可以讀到有懶音"},{"pid":"f5c34302f95f9c8e02c0564521d269577449397e","tid":1033932,"uid":90820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6d2fcb28d0f2eb8fce116917d4504c212617b3c8","tid":1033932,"uid":11598,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3d1ea49ed78f77b70be1e53435c5e04ce919df19","tid":1033932,"uid":90820,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T14:26:42.000Z","msg":"但香港有班人連粵語都講唔正<br />\n淨係睇連登留言都知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你<span style=\"color: red;\">起</span>邊度？<br />\n係<span style=\"color: red;\">味</span>咁樣